**Observed result after the fix**:
After all restart recovery retries are exhausted, any session still stuck with stale abortedLastRun flag has it cleared. The session can then process new incoming messages normally, eliminating the permanent busy state. No side effects on running sessions.

**What was not tested**:
No live gateway restart tested in production environment. The fix only clears a stale boolean flag when recovery retries are exhausted, with no risks to active sessions.
